  "subject": "CI: Move helm builds to larger instance",
  "commit_message": "CI: Move helm builds to larger instance\n\nInstead of specifying a VOLUME_SIZE and causing the cloud to generate a\nvolume from the boot image, we should be launching directly against the\nboot image. To get the same (or in this case larger) disk we need to\nbump up the flavor size to achieve our goals.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Id6c2d6f0ef8ac84480d155e592e82b7aeddad286\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Grimberg <agrimberg@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
